cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use this software, please cite it as below."
title: "wickra-copilot"
abstract: >-
  A local market copilot built on the Wickra core: a data-driven ContextSpec is
  folded over serialized microstructure feeds (order book, trades, funding, open
  interest, liquidations) into a deterministic MarketContext of hard facts (price
  moves, order-book imbalance, liquidation clusters, funding flips, OI changes,
  volatility spikes), grounding a language model in real market data. Exposed as a
  JSON-over-C-ABI data API in ten languages, with a separate, swappable LLM
  adapter.
type: software
authors:
